WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.775 line:0%
 
KNOWN AS BILLY THE KID.

00:00:08.809 --> 00:00:12.112
AS AN ADOLESCENT,
HE STOLE CHEESE,

00:00:12.145 --> 00:00:14.581
AND THEN HE GOT ARRESTED.

00:00:14.615 --> 00:00:17.050
AND HE ESCAPED
OUT OF AN OUTHOUSE.

00:00:17.084 --> 00:00:20.988
THAT'S WHEN HE FELT LIKE
HE WAS AN OUTLAW.

00:00:22.055 --> 00:00:24.491
YOU KNOW, THESE--
THESE RANCH OWNERS

00:00:24.525 --> 00:00:26.593
AND THESE LAND OWNERS
AND THESE SHERIFFS

00:00:26.627 --> 00:00:29.730
WERE TAKING WATER AND LAND
AND MONEY

00:00:29.763 --> 00:00:31.765
FROM THE INDIANS,
THE MEXICANS.

00:00:31.798 --> 00:00:34.268
AND BILLY THE KID
IS THE KIND OF GUY

00:00:34.301 --> 00:00:35.936
THAT WOULD BE LIKE,
[bleep] YOU.

00:00:35.969 --> 00:00:39.006
YOU'RE NOT GONNA DO THAT.

00:00:39.039 --> 00:00:40.841
I'M GONNA SHOOT YOU
AND KILL YOUR PEOPLE...

00:00:40.874 --> 00:00:42.809
BOOM, BOOM, BOOM.
BOOM, BOOM.

00:00:42.843 --> 00:00:44.344
AND YOUR SHERIFFS, MAYBE.

00:00:44.378 --> 00:00:46.413
PEW, PEW, PEW.

00:00:46.446 --> 00:00:49.583
HE WAS LOVED
BY THE HISPANIC COMMUNITY,

00:00:49.616 --> 00:00:50.817
AND HE APPARENTLY HAD

00:00:50.851 --> 00:00:54.188
A LOT OF LATINA WOMEN
THAT LOVED HIM.

00:00:54.221 --> 00:00:57.891
BUT, UH--
[laughs]

00:00:57.925 --> 00:00:59.059
- DID HE DATE ANY?

00:00:59.092 --> 00:01:00.427
- OH, A LOT OF 'EM.

00:01:00.460 --> 00:01:02.429
HE LOVED LATINA WOMEN.

00:01:04.097 --> 00:01:05.666 line:0%
 
THERE WAS THESE STORIES
WHERE HE KILLED

00:01:05.699 --> 00:01:07.634 line:0%
 
THESE PEOPLE, LIKE,
UH, JOE GRANT,

00:01:07.668 --> 00:01:10.070 line:0%
 
WHO WAS THE LOCAL DRUNK,
APPARENTLY, AT THIS BAR.

00:01:10.070 --> 00:01:11.338
AND BILLY THE KID
WAS SITTING THERE

00:01:11.371 --> 00:01:12.706
AND HE DIDN'T RECOGNIZE HIM.

00:01:12.739 --> 00:01:14.508
HE SAID, IF I--
IF I MET BILLY THE KID,

00:01:14.541 --> 00:01:16.109
I WOULD KILL HIM
IN COLD BLOOD.

00:01:16.143 --> 00:01:17.177
I'D MURDER HIM.

00:01:17.211 --> 00:01:19.813
AND HE WAS LIKE,
OKAY.

00:01:19.847 --> 00:01:22.516
AND SO BILLY THE KID,
HE SAID,

00:01:22.549 --> 00:01:24.818
MAN, I LOVE
YOUR IVORY HANDLE.

00:01:24.852 --> 00:01:26.453
AND HE TURNED IT
TO WHERE THERE WAS

00:01:26.486 --> 00:01:29.656
ONE BLANK
ON THAT REVOLVER.

00:01:29.690 --> 00:01:33.493
AND HE SAID, HEY, JOE GRANT,
I'M BILLY THE KID.

00:01:33.527 --> 00:01:35.629
[ominous music]

00:01:35.662 --> 00:01:38.098
OH, REALLY?
AND HE WALKED OUT.

00:01:38.131 --> 00:01:40.200
AND YOU HEAR--
[click]

00:01:40.234 --> 00:01:42.436
AND THEN BILLY THE KID
TURNED AROUND

00:01:42.469 --> 00:01:45.005
AND SHOT THAT DUDE
IN THE CHIN.

00:01:45.105 --> 00:01:46.473
[chuckles]
IN THE CHIN.

00:01:46.507 --> 00:01:48.308
I MEAN, WELL,
YOU'RE AN ASS[bleep].

00:01:48.342 --> 00:01:49.443
BOOM, BOOM, BOOM.

00:01:49.476 --> 00:01:50.777
[playing piano]

00:01:50.811 --> 00:01:53.680
AND WHAT'S CRAZY
ABOUT BILLY THE KID,

00:01:53.714 --> 00:01:56.783
HE COULD SING IN A WAY
THAT NO ONE ELSE COULD SING.

00:01:56.817 --> 00:01:57.818
[singing poorly]

00:01:57.851 --> 00:01:58.819
LET'S--TRY THAT.

00:01:58.852 --> 00:02:02.689
[gibberish]

00:02:02.723 --> 00:02:04.391
[laughs]

00:02:04.424 --> 00:02:05.759
[mumbling]

00:02:05.792 --> 00:02:07.728
HEY, BITCH!

00:02:07.761 --> 00:02:10.664
[laughs]

00:02:10.697 --> 00:02:14.234
I'M, LIKE, A BITCH!

00:02:14.268 --> 00:02:16.103
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

00:02:16.136 --> 00:02:18.939
[laughs]

00:02:18.972 --> 00:02:21.708
PAT GARRETT WAS THE SHERIFF
AND SAID,

00:02:21.742 --> 00:02:25.279
MY--MY ONE GOAL IS TO GET--

00:02:25.312 --> 00:02:28.315
I'M GONNA GET BILLY THE KID.

00:02:30.284 --> 00:02:32.719
AND HE HUNTED DOWN
BILLY THE KID.

00:02:32.753 --> 00:02:35.088
SO THEY FOUND HIM
IN A FARMHOUSE,

00:02:35.122 --> 00:02:37.424
AND THEY HAD THE WHOLE PLACE
SURROUNDED.

00:02:37.457 --> 00:02:41.328
ONE GUY CAME OUT AND HE DECIDED
TO GO FEED THE HORSE,

00:02:41.361 --> 00:02:42.362
AND THEY SHOT HIM DOWN

00:02:42.396 --> 00:02:43.830
AND THOUGHT THAT
IT WAS BILLY THE KID.

00:02:43.864 --> 00:02:46.099
AND THEY WERE LIKE, WE GOT
BILLY THE KID, WE GOT HIM.

00:02:46.099 --> 00:02:47.868
AND THEN THEY REALIZED
THAT IT WASN'T HIM.

00:02:47.901 --> 00:02:49.503
SO THEN THEY REALIZED
IT WASN'T HIM.

00:02:49.536 --> 00:02:50.838
AND PAT GARRETT SAID,
WELL, SHOOT THE HORSE DOWN.

00:02:50.871 --> 00:02:51.972
SHOOT THE HORSE DOWN.

00:02:52.005 --> 00:02:54.107
THERE'S NO WINDOWS.
THERE'S NO EXIT.

00:02:54.107 --> 00:02:57.377
AND SO THEY
SHOT THE HORSE DOWN.

00:02:57.411 --> 00:02:59.246
AND THEY PUT THE HORSE,
THE DEAD HORSE,

00:02:59.279 --> 00:03:01.415
IN FRONT OF THE EXIT.

00:03:01.448 --> 00:03:03.283
AND THEY PUT HIM
IN FRONT OF THE EXIT

00:03:03.317 --> 00:03:07.087
AND NO ONE ELSE
COULD GET OUT.

